Stanislas Merhar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanislas_Merhar 0 Stanislas Merhar (born 24 January 1971) is a French actor.He was born in Paris in a family of immigrants from Slovenia. He works in cinema, television and theatre.In 1998 Merhar won the César Award for Most Promising Actor for his role in the film Dry Cleaning.
